snippet.title: Beetle Junior DS - Nintendo DS Gameplay
snippet.description:
While this is known on PC as Beetle Bug 2 (or Beetle Ju 2), this is a pretty interesting one, as it's the only game in the series to ever get a console release. In this case, this is a port of Beetle Bug 2 for the Nintendo DS, under the name Beetle Junior DS.

Beetle Bug / Beetle Ju, Beetle Junior DS (C) gamigo AG
